═══════ 01_trait.mojo ═══════
=== MOJO-10: Trait / parametric polymorphism ===

[1] 단일 trait bound — render(Drawable)]
[Circle.draw] r= 3.0
[Square.draw] s= 5.0

[2] 다중 trait bound — describe(Drawable & Stringable)]
describe: Circle(7.0)
[Circle.draw] r= 7.0

[3] trait 상속 — Pet은 Animal의 contract도 만족]
[Dog.sound] Rex → woof
[Dog.sound] Rex → woof
  owner: Alice

[정리]
  trait T = C++ concept
  struct Foo(T1, T2) = struct Foo conforms to T1 and T2
  fn f[T: Trait](x: T) = template<Trait T> + 컴파일 시점 monomorphization
  fn f[T: A & B](x: T) = 다중 concept requires (C++20)
  trait Pet(Animal) = trait inheritance (Rust 'trait Pet: Animal')
  abstract method body는 '...'로 표기 (Python '...'와 같은 위치, 의미는 'unimplemented')

